      "text": "SOUND=SPACE is an electronic musical instrument that is played - by one person or several at the same time - by moving around in an empty space. ",
      "id": "2defb5ccbccc2895",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "text": "It consists of a system of ultrasonic sensors that very accurately picks up the positions and movement of people within the space, linked to a computer and a synthesiser and/or sampler that produces sounds accordingly - [http://www.gehlhaar.org/x/pages/soundspace.htm gelhaar.org]",
      "id": "85dcb012508bc12b",
